{"id":122,"idInBook":4248,"chapterId":22,"bookId":14,"arabic":"وَعَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ قَالَ: لَقَدْ رَأَيْتُ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ مُلَبِّدًا. رَوَاهُ البُخَارِيّ","english":{"narrator":"","text":"Ibn ‘Umar said he had seen God’s messenger with matted hair. \nBukhari transmitted it."},"hadithNumber":4248,"hadithId":122,"reference":"22:122","meta":{"id":"mishkat_almasabih","length":4428,"totalChapters":25,"arabic":{"title":"مشكاة المصابيح","author":"الإمام الكاتب التبريزي"},"english":{"title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","author":"Al-Khatib Al-Tabrizi"}},"chapter":{"id":22,"bookId":14,"arabic":"كتاب اللباس","english":"Clothing","startHadith":4127,"endHadith":4319,"totalHadiths":193},"version":{"name":"mishkat_almasabih","title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","chapters":25}}